### SireneSearchController — Manual test requests
### Prerequisite: obtain an association JWT and set it below.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@assoToken = <paste_association_jwt_here>

### 1. Search by SIREN (expect 200 with simplified DTO)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/association/sirene/search?q=775685019
Authorization: Bearer {{assoToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 2. Search by SIRET (expect 200 with simplified DTO including address/city)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/association/sirene/search?q=77568501900016
Authorization: Bearer {{assoToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Invalid format — too short (expect 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/association/sirene/search?q=123
Authorization: Bearer {{assoToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. Valid format but unknown identifier (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/association/sirene/search?q=000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{assoToken}}
Accept: application/json
